high_descs: Turn around and walk to the right then turn left and walk to the desk.
Pick up the metal box that is on top of the desk.
Turn right then turn left and walk around to the other side of the desk. Turn right to face the desk.
Use the metal box to turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn on a lamp with a metal box.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the side of the wooden desk
Pick up the alarm clock from the desk
Walk forward around to the right side of the desk
Turn on the lamp on the desk
anns.task_desc: Examine the alarm clock under the light of the desk lamp

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the the desk behind the wall, to your left.
Pick up the alarm clock, on the desk, in front of the blue chair.
Walk past the desk and turn left, then go to the lamp on the end of the desk, by the wall.
Turn on the lamp in the front, right corner of the desk.
